thread.title: ELIZABETH
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by ELIZABETH

author: ELIZABETH
title: ELIZABETH
text: All areas of the rental were excellent, car clean ready on time and courteous reception on return of vehicle. Special mention of the young lady at the Melbourne Airport counter on collection of the vehicle.... she is an asset to your company. Not sure of her name but think it was Shaz. We will be back.
